Syntax Notes
Correct Entity Declaration:

xml
<!DOCTYPE root [<!ENTITY name SYSTEM "URI">]>
Entity Reference:

xml
<element>&name;</element>
Important Syntax Rules:

Entity names cannot contain spaces

Always use semicolon after entity reference

DOCTYPE must come after XML declaration

Root element must match application expectations

