Troubleshooting Notes
Common Error 1: Duplicate Tags


Problem: <stockCheck>...</stockCheck><storeId>3</storeId></stockCheck>
Fix: Remove duplicate tags, ensure single root element
Common Error 2: Missing Semicolon


Problem: &xxe
Fix: Use &xxe;
Common Error 3: Wrong File Path


Linux: /etc/passwd (no file:// prefix sometimes)
Windows: c:/windows/win.ini (not C:\windows\win.ini)
File Path Cheatsheet
Linux:


/etc/passwd
/etc/shadow
/etc/hosts
/var/www/html/config.php
/home/[user]/.ssh/id_rsa
/proc/self/environ
Windows:


c:/windows/win.ini
c:/windows/system32/drivers/etc/hosts
c:/inetpub/wwwroot/web.config
Protocols Available

file:// - Local file system
http:// - HTTP requests
https:// - HTTPS requests
ftp:// - FTP requests
